| Threat ID | Category | Component | Disposition | Mitigation Plan |
|-----------|----------|-----------|-------------|-----------------|
| T-32-01 | Tampering/DoS | D3DAssemble parsing malformed/oversized .vsh source in the probe | 
accept | Probe is a one-shot offline diagnostic over trusted, version-pinned extracted assets; no 
