| `#include` resolution (TRE-archived `.inc`) | gl05/gl07 plugin (`IncludeHandler::Open` :144) | 
`TreeFile` (sharedFile) | Engine already routes includes through TreeFile, not Win32 FS |
| Reauthored `vs_2_0` HLSL overrides | `stage/override/vertex_program/*.vsh` (loose files) | 
`client.cfg` searchPath | gl11 already ships these; they shadow the TRE `//asm` originals for the 
HLSL path |
| Compiled bytecode â†’ `IDirect3DVertexShader9` | gl05/gl07 plugin (`CreateVertexShader` :573) | 
