| Non-compile D3DX (mesh/matrix/surface) | gl05/gl07 plugin (`Direct3d9.cpp`, `_RenderTarget.cpp`, 
`_TextureData.cpp`) | â€” | OUT OF SCOPE (D-05); stays linked this phase |

