`AdditionalDependencies` of gl05/gl07 vcxproj; resolves from Windows Kit `Lib/.../um/x86/`. 
[VERIFIED: vcxproj grep + WK x86 lib exists] |
| `Direct3d11_HlslRewrite` (logic) | in-tree, Phase 11 | Rules A/B/C/D/E/F textual rewrite â€” the 
