| A5 | Dropping `register(vN)` from DECLARE_textureCoordinateSets is safe for D3D9 input binding | 
Pattern 3, Pitfall 3 | MEDIUM â€” likely the WIP branch's render-incompleteness root cause. Under 
D3D9 the vertex declaration drives binding, but the inline register may still matter. Test in the 
Tatooine smoke. |
| A6 | d3dcompiler.lib already in the link path makes D3DCompile/D3DAssemble link cleanly | Standard 
